ar. (23) He grinned at Chatterer in the most provoking way. (24) It made Chatterer angry just to see him. (25) So said Reddy Fox, knowing all the time that Chatterer couldn't take a walk with any one. (26) At first Chatterer scolded and called Reddy all the bad names he could think of, but after a little he didn't feel so much like scolding. (27) In fact, he didn't half hear the mean things Reddy Fox said to him.



